OL,3,CSign language law has brought
OL,4,Csignificant benefits to deaf people `
OL,5,Ccommittee
OL,7,FA sign language law passed a decade
OL,8,Fago has "brought significant benefits"
OL,9,Fto deaf people, a Holyrood committee
OL,10,Fhas said, but MSPs are "concerned"
OL,11,Fabout a lack of access for young
OL,12,Fpeople.
OL,14,FThe British Sign Language (Scotland)
OL,15,FAct was passed in 2015, mandating the
OL,16,FScottish Government and councils to
OL,17,Fcome up with plans to widen access to
OL,18,Fthe language.
