OL,3,CSign language law has brought
OL,4,Csignificant benefits to deaf people `
OL,5,Ccommittee
OL,7,FA new report by the Equalities, Human
OL,8,FRights and Civil Justice Committee at
OL,9,FHolyrood has found the law has
OL,10,Fimproved the lives of deaf people
OL,11,Facross the country.
OL,13,FBut the MSPs have also stressed the
OL,14,Fneed to improve the situation in
OL,15,Fschools, as well as a lack of
OL,16,Fqualified BSL interpreters in Scotland.
