OL,3,CSign language law has brought
OL,4,Csignificant benefits to deaf people `
OL,5,Ccommittee
OL,7,F"It is clear that the Act has brought
OL,8,Fsignificant benefits to BSL users in
OL,9,FScotland, including increased
OL,10,Fvisibility of the language, improved
OL,11,Faccess to services, and greater
OL,12,Fempowerment of the deaf community,"
OL,13,Fthe report said.
OL,15,FIt added: "The committee is
OL,16,Fparticularly concerned about the
OL,17,Fexperiences of deaf children and young
OL,18,Fpeople, especially in education and
OL,19,Fearly years provision, and the
OL,20,Fbarriers they face in accessing their
OL,21,Fnative language.
