OL,3,CSign language law has brought
OL,4,Csignificant benefits to deaf people `
OL,5,Ccommittee
OL,7,F"The importance of deaf role models,
OL,8,Fqualified teachers, and inclusive
OL,9,Flearning environments cannot be
OL,10,Foverstated.
OL,12,F"The committee strongly agrees on the
OL,13,Fimportance of providing access to the
OL,14,Flearning of BSL from an early age,
OL,15,Fboth for deaf and hearing children and
OL,16,Fconsiders that without significantly
OL,17,Fexpanding the pool of individuals with
OL,18,Fknowledge of the language, the
OL,19,Fshortage of qualified interpreters is
OL,20,Funlikely to be resolved."
