OL,5,Ccommittee
OL,7,FThe lack of qualified teachers and
OL,8,Finterpreters, the report added, was
OL,9,Fhaving a "direct impact on children's
OL,10,Flearning".
OL,12,FThe report made a number of
OL,13,Frecommendations, including urging the
OL,14,FGovernment to lay out how it will
OL,15,Fincrease the number of teachers and
OL,16,Fwhat investments it will make, as well
OL,17,Fas calling for BSL to have "parity of
OL,18,Festeem" with other minority languages
OL,19,Flike Gaelic.
