OL,3,CSign language law has brought
OL,4,Csignificant benefits to deaf people `
OL,5,Ccommittee
OL,7,FCommittee convener Karen Adam said the
OL,8,Flaw had been "transformational", but
OL,9,Fprogress had been "uneven and
OL,10,Fsubstantial challenges remain".
OL,12,F"For many deaf people, BSL is not an
OL,13,Fadditional language but their only
OL,14,Flanguage," she said.
OL,16,F"That's why we want to see the
OL,17,FScottish Government and public bodies
OL,18,Fcontinue with their commitment to
OL,19,Fconsulting on and improving their
OL,20,Fsupport for BSL users."
